cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the task of image inpainting, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves using deep neural networks to model the inference and translation steps, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions using heuristics to guide the propagation of local textures, which could be considered as a graphics-related aspect (cs.GR). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method involves comparing it to previous state-of-the-art methods, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
